# - Try to find the MakeNSIS
# Once done this will define
#
#  MAKENSIS_FOUND - system has MakeNSIS
#  MAKENSIS - the MakeNSIS program
#  MAKENSIS_FLAGS - the MakeNSIS flags
#  MAKENSIS_SUFFIX - the MakeNSIS output file suffix

